      • main

        public static void main​(java.lang.String[] args)
        The main Program starts by trying to read the file. If this fails an error message is printed to the console and the program exits. If it succeeds then the read data are used to generate a heatmap. Afterwards it attempts to write the generated heatmap to a file in a geojson form. If it fails then it just prints it out to the console.
        Parameters:
        args - - It should be the full path to the file needed for processing.
